WEBVTT

00:10:59.000 --> 00:11:01.856
why one in four people

00:11:01.880 --> 00:11:06.736
receives excessive or unwanted
medical treatment,

00:11:06.760 --> 00:11:11.920
or watches a family member receive
excessive or unwanted medical treatment.

00:11:13.600 --> 00:11:15.696
It's not because doctors don't get it.

00:11:15.720 --> 00:11:16.920
We do.

00:11:17.520 --> 00:11:20.456
We understand the real
psychological consequences

00:11:20.480 --> 00:11:22.840
on patients and their families.

00:11:23.760 --> 00:11:25.600
The things is, we deal with them, too.

00:11:26.720 --> 00:11:32.056
Half of critical care nurses
and a quarter of ICU doctors